          "anchor" : "overview",
          "level" : 2,
          "text" : "Overview",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "The Swift extension provides language features such as code completion and jump to definition via ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier" : "https:\/\/github.com\/apple\/sourcekit-lsp",
              "isActive" : true,
              "type" : "reference"
            },
            {
              "text" : ".",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content" : [
            {
              "inlineContent" : [
                {
                  "text" : "With Swift toolchains prior to 6.1 you will need to build your project at least once for SourceKit-LSP to function correcly. Whenever you add a new dependency to your project, make sure to rebuild it so that SourceKit-LSP can update its information.",
                  "type" : "text"
                }
              ],
              "type" : "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name" : "⚠️ Important",
          "style" : "note",
          "type" : "aside"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "SourceKit-LSP provides background indexing in Swift toolchain 6.1 which will automatically index your project on startup. All indexing results are cached in the ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : ".build\/index-build",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " folder within your workspace.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Language features are common to all VS Code extensions. See the ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier" : "https:\/\/code.visualstudio.com\/docs\/editing\/editingevolved",
              "isActive" : true,
              "type" : "reference"
            },
            {
              "text" : " for a more in-depth overview.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "SourceKit-LSP can be configured via extension settings. See ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier" : "doc:\/\/userdocs\/documentation\/userdocs\/settings",
              "isActive" : true,
              "type" : "reference"
            },
            {
              "text" : " for more information.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind" : "content"
    }
  ],
